summary: I opened for Taylor Swift at her 1989 London show and got to hang out with her afterwards. To me, she’s probably one of the...
text: I opened for Taylor Swift at her 1989 London show and got to hang out with her afterwards. To me, she’s probably one of the biggest stars of our generation and also had a huge influence on the way I write pop music, so I had to try sooo hard to keep my cool. I just remember looking down at her feet and thinking ‘wow she even has the most amazing pop star feet’ hahaha. Love y, u Taylor.
source: Lauren Aquilina about meeting and being starstruck by Taylor - MTV (April 10th 2019)

There was no better time for this to happen than during Long Live, I’ll always be there screaming your name from the sidelines Taylor - and I can’t wait to do it all over again next time ❤️

@taylorswift @taylornation
